{"tid":1357324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【提示】防止被帶風向，睇post請先睇尾","createTime":"2019-07-23T16:44:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T18:38:03.000Z","uid":176447,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0e91a7b8ca504e6c437e6954c7b4139d8555bcfa","tid":1357324,"uid":176447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:44:08.000Z","msg":"鑑於近日大量以訛傳訛，風向，山埃，炒車post排山倒海而來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而此類post經常正負評及頭幾頁風向與往後之討論大相逕庭，極度誤導大量冇追post嘅巴絲打同cd rom<br />\n<br />\n所以，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我呼籲大家睇post請先由尾幾版睇起 先再睇返正文 以清晰思考<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">連登有便利方法跳至尾頁</span><br />\napp版可於目錄長按post名<br />\n網頁版(電腦/流動) 可以用post名尾嘅頁數drop down<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外亦可善用閃電掣</span>(正負評總數排列)<br />\n<br />\n請大家養成習慣 避免消息混亂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3afbbaed26ace343f6044a5518df42782d3044","tid":1357324,"uid":176447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:48:19.000Z","msg":"727<br />\n我冇野講<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe688d09b551e5e1406b64d85580468db306c836","tid":1357324,"uid":176447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:56:48.000Z","msg":"仲有善用google 搵post<br />\n而家search function 啲post多到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以再用埋時間限制收窄範圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c6926d60d5bbc2db8dc71a0f285ffdedbad8db","tid":1357324,"uid":145736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:58:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0316d2b56faa15e12e816b279622f54d010b59fa","tid":1357324,"uid":114537,